item.title: About
item.description: I am Pepe Márquez Romero a computer science student based in Madrid. Education Universidad Politécnica de Madrid, School of Computer Science. Experience I am learning Java and C in the university degree. I have started developing in Rust since Summer 2020. I have stated developing in Python since March 2020. I have done great contributions to open-source projects. Open Source projects weather_bot.
